title: ID_Interactable_DeskButton_Interacted_ENG
---
Daniel: (<Italic>This... Looks like a button. But why should a button be here?</>) #tone:question
Daniel: (<Italic>Maybe it's connected to some kind of mechanism, but who knows if it still works after the fire.</>) #tone:thinking
Daniel: (<Italic>If I push it, it doesn't move... But what if I found something with the same shape?</>) #tone:thinking
===

title: ID_Interactable_DeskButton_NotSolved_ENG
---
