title: ID_Interactable_DeskButton_Solved_ENG
---
Daniel: (<Italic>...! It worked!</>) #tone:surprised
Daniel: (<Italic>So the candlestick was the solution... Ironic.</>) #tone:sarcastic
Daniel: (<Italic>Now the drawer's open. I should look inside.</>) #tone:serious
