title: ID_Interactable_DresserLock_Interacted_ENG
---
Daniel: (<Italic>Melissa locked this drawer with a locker...? There's really no worst way to hide something.</>) #tone:sigh
Daniel: (<Italic>It has a 4-digit combination, with numbers going from 1 to 9. But I have no idea what's the combination.</>) #tone:thinking
Daniel: (<Italic>That girl may be unbearable, but she's not stupid. Whatever is the solution, it won't be easy to find it.</>) #tone:thinking
===

title: ID_Interactable_DresserLock_NotSolved_ENG
---
Daniel: (<Italic>Wrong combination.</>) #tone:sigh
===

title: ID_Interactable_DresserLock_Solved_ENG
---
Daniel: (<Italic>Oh! It's open. 6253... Is it a date?</>) #tone:surprised
Daniel: (<Italic>Doesn't matter. Now, let's see what's inside.</>) #tone:serious
===

title: ID_Interactable_DresserLock_AlreadySolved_ENG
---
Daniel: (<Italic>It wasn't easy to find the solution. I guess that's what they mean when they say "don't judge a book by its cover".</>) #tone:sigh
